title.rendered: DASH OFFROAD  Y62 Patrol Under Body Protection

content.rendered:
DASH OFFROAD Y62 Patrol Under Body Protection

To Suit: Y62 Patrol Series 1, 2, 3, 4, 5

Construction: CAD designed – CNC cut, 4 piece to offer full protection to radiator, sump, transmission and transfer case. Window access to oil filter and large hole to easily access sump plug. Made from 3mm manganese steel which is renowned for its high impact strength, light weight and resistance to abrasion. This is not just a piece of metal folded up in a shed, this has been fully engineered to keep weight down and strength to a maximum.

Total weight: 28kg.

Surface: Matte Black
